    [OSStructureField(Description = "A list of [Commission State tabs][cc]. A Commission County tab displays the state in which a notary's commission was granted. This tab can only be assigned to a remote notary recipient using [Docusign Notary][notary]. The tab's value can be edited by the recipient. [cc]:  /docs/esign-rest-api/reference/envelopes/enveloperecipienttabs/ [notary]: /docs/notary-api/", OriginalName = "commissionStateTabs")]
